               <p>WILLIAM HENRY HUGHES. I <rs id="t18271206-151-viclabel799" type="occupation">keep a book shop</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18271206-151-victim860 t18271206-151-viclabel799"></join>, at <placeName id="t18271206-151-crimeloc800">No. 1, Red Lion-street, Holborn</placeName>
